Bell Cablemedia Q1 net loss widens . Quarter to March 31 ( million stg unless stated ) Net loss 49 . 7 vs 19 . 5 loss Turnover 46 . 2 vs 16 . 0NOTE - Net loss per American Depositary Share was 62p versus a loss of 31p . The company attributed the increased net loss to higher depreciation and amortisation costs and increased interest expense . Q1 1997 results include Videotron , which was acquired in December . Bell Cablemedia Plc was one of the companies to be merged into Cable and Wireless Communications , a unit of Cable and Wireless Plc . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7717 
